channel.title: Tyden 562/668 V2
channel.description:
[CENTER][size=24pt]Tyden 562/668 V2[/size]
[B][size=12pt]Introduction[/size][/B] [B] Tyden 562/668 is a project to bring back the 562/668 servers! This server will have a much better features(combat, clipping, etc) than the ones in the orig 562/659+ server release.
The base will be a cleaned rs2hd with barely any content in it and my goal is to program all of the necessary features in it! This is more of a great learning experience for me but when i finish, i will host this.
Some may know me from my old tyden 562 project: [url=http://www.google.com/forums/showthread.php?78597-Tyden-562-668]http://www.google.com/forums/showthread.php?78597-Tyden-562-668[/url]
I realised how shitty it was and i decided to start on a clean base this time. It will take more time, but it will be much better. Trust me. [/B]
[B]BASE: RS2HD with barely any content(Incomplete combat, no food, etc.)[/B]
[U]Update(s) in progress: [/U] Economy(Trading, Shops, skills etc) [s]Rewriting the combat[/s] [s]Finding a good 562/668 client and making it work properly with server[/s]
[CODE] Features NPC updating Player Updating Multiplayer support Decen Entity based combat NPC and Player clipping Woodcutting Projectile Clipping + more will update later. [/CODE]
More updates before 21 of feb was made. Forgot them tho. NOTE: Updates are updated throughout the day
[U][B]Feb 21, 2013[/B][/U]
Downloaded Titanpk's 562/668 client and cache Made adjustments to the server so it could connect [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/J10z6LG.png[/img]
[U][B]Feb 22, 2013[/B][/U]
Made a simple skills system Woodcutting has been added Combat timers were adjusted Loading items from cache Implemented proper hitsplats Fixed all client related issues Added lumbridge npc spawns Implemented prayers HD has been fixed [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/K6LLnMs.png[/img]
[U][B]Feb 23, 2013[/B][/U]
668 maps Proper hitmarks. You can tell if its ur hit or not. Emotes have been completed by me. Food has been completed Basic combat has been written. VERY BASIC Player following has been added Poison base has been coded Projectile clipping! Instant special attacks have been coded(Gmaul,dbaxe) Potions have been completed Finished special npc combat system(Converted blink. Creds to rs4life) [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/UZtzzIG.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/KzusF3W.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/7mSMZ7P.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/mmThU5D.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/XocAMs7.png[/img]
[U][B]Feb 24, 2013[/B][/U] Soaking has been completed Torva now increases your max hp Enabled blooming on client Added poison to every weapon with a (p) suffix Vengance Rewrote the magic manager Added sounds [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/vWLv9Xh.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/auiWUvA.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/bvaj2Oc.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/nxByxT0.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/xZWgVMu.jpg[/img]
[U][B]Feb 25, 2013[/B][/U] Phonex necklace added Recoil ring added Protection Prayer delay(Preventing player from turning on prayer for awhile) Proper prayer draining(prayer bonuses included) Staff of light special Veng fully completed Spirit shield effects have been added Overload has been fixed + few more combat bugs [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/v9Slf4d.png[/img]
[U][B]March 2, 2013[/B][/U] Fixed smite prayer draining Added full vine whip special attack Implemented character design [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/FWb0QcY.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/eCp2u1M.png[/img] [img]http://i.imgur.com/Pvn7hCo.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/V9QR47l.png[/img]
[U][B]March 8, 2013[/B][/U] Added actual prayer points instead of just multiplying the player's prayer level by 10 Added all super potions Arrows now have a 20% chance of dropping on the ground Minor combat bugs have been fixed Woodcutting has been taken out. Will be rewritten later.
[U][B]March 10 , 2013[/B][/U]
[ul]Fixed equipment interface added equipping and unequipping Finished trading, things left: total wealth, lending and icon flashing Added item examines Fully fixed trading, added cheap total wealth Fully finished price checker Finished shops [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/xHGDM65.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/ztquW9R.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i.imgur.com/WXs36x5.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/yXAURvx.png[/img]
[U][B]March 11 , 2013[/B][/U] Added npc and player drops Made a cutscene system, found 2 of the camera packets and dynamic region and now I can make smexy cutscenes Finished burying bones Added more bolt specials(Onxy and ruby) [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/JP3OoOJ.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/T70MHwW.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/8uKIUiN.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/XceAZcU.png[/img]
[U][B]March 12 , 2013[/B][/U] [list] [*]Bank Tabs [*]fixed dupes with trading and shops [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/0G1RNjY.png[/img]
[U][B]March 13 , 2013[/B][/U] [list] [*]More bank tab fixes [*]Firemaking and pickpocketing have been completed [*]Base for summoning has been made. [*]Ban/Ipban has been implemented [*]Various bug fixes around the base [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/miUbUHQ.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/zWx34Ep.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/uaP4oBb.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/DdMwbQX.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/pK2Mnvj.png[/img]
[U][B]March 16 , 2013[/B][/U] [list] [*]High item alching [*]Summonning left-click option customization [*]Castle wars base has been started on TODO: Sending correct interface settings, bandages, underground tunnel, hinticons [*]Other various bug fixes [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/OqLk1Pa.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/nMxGuka.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/xFshRiE.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/YLyceTM.png[/img]
[U][B]March 23, 2013[/B][/U] [list] [*]Removed castle wars for now [*]Implemented hint icons [*]Finished all god war bosses [*]Nex Combat has been started on[Converted from old Tyden) [*]Various bug fixes [*]Moved home to canfis [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/zrTQdW2.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/m7HUtKk.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/2ysJA02.png[/img]
March 30, 2013 [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/qitwE1r.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/7nHNLOX.png[/img]
[U][B]April 18 , 2013[/B][/U] [list] [*]Fixed various bugs relating to combat and familiar during private testing [*]Finished Kalphite Queen [*]Fully finished familiars vs player [*]Tweaked the client's hitsplats to look nicer [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/aDhme91.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/YfaDnue.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/7P26dif.png[/img]
